Class SwipingSession

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.avaje.ebean.Model
      • models.SwipingSession

  • public class SwipingSession
extends com.avaje.ebean.Model
    An entity representing a swiping session between a set of users. Apart from having a set of users associated with it, each swiping session also keeps track of their chosen activities.

      • findByEmail

        public static java.util.List<SwipingSession> findByEmail(java.util.List<java.lang.String> emails)
        Method to get all swiping sessions where all of the users and exactly those users associate with the passed email addresses have taken part. That is, will only return those swiping sessions whose set of users are exactly equal to those indicated by the email addresses.
        Parameters:
        emails - a list of emails to match swiping sessions against.
        Returns:
        a list of swiping sessions that are associated with exactly those users indicated by the email addresses passed.
